Hey, where are all the Musky???  :-)
nice, how cold was the water??
Ouch! When we hitting the big water???
Matt wanted to go tomorrow but heavy sw winds were thinking perch on Simcoe. Back to being a weekend warrior after this week Rod(good thing Lake O is huge)

Not sure of the wisdom of these dives, but the water is pretty clear, reminds of when I was like 20 in the 70's and started  diving -would dive most anywhere any time-dove the buffalo coin pile one year and off brockville and prescott numerous times - lots of carp in the shadows- but I hear the water is a lot clearer now due to zebra mussles
Rob, now look what you've started........  OK Matt, we'll hit LSC and see if I can't change that!
